  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;Within two months of the date of this decision, the following structures shall be removed in their entirety and the fabric of the building made good to the satisfaction of&amp;nbsp; the local planning authority:-&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;i) dormer window;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;ii) satellite dish located on the chimney; and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;iii) the front roof light to the south elevation.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within two months of the date of this decision, the roof lights in the north and east elevations shall be replaced with conservation-type roof lights that are flush with the roof slope to the satisfaction of the local planning authority.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Reason: To comply with the enforcement notice&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;2017/0383/ENF in the interests of the visual amenities of the surrounding area.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;The total noise level from fixed mechanical extraction system shall be 10 dB(A) or more below the measured LA90 background noise level at the nearest noise-sensitive premises at any time.&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-a39dafe6-7fff-d0c3-8ef2-4f30d716144a&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;REASON: In order to safeguard the amenities of surrounding occupiers and the area generally&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
